# Standalone build dir (own target dir — links the ~300-MiB verified Lean
# closure; ~1.5 GiB of build artifacts, never the shared ./target). The PD ELF
# (dregg-executor-microkit-pd.elf, ~374 MiB) lives under here too — a build
# output, regenerated by `make -C sel4 build-executor-microkit`.
/target
Cargo.lock

# NOTE: microkit-patch/ IS tracked — the one-function microkit-tool patch + the
# prebuilt patched tool + the boot evidence are the keystone's reproducibility
# artifacts (the tool change that lets the 5-PD image BOOT), not build outputs.
